item.title: By: Ben
item.dc:creator: Ben
item.description: Oh man... that's definitely rough. Did you tell them to bring you back something from Congress though? Baduktopia should be there, so they should get you Lee Sedol's new second book. =P And on that note, I hear that Go Congress 2014 might be in NYC! So we should try to go! =)
item.content:encoded:
Oh man… that’s definitely rough. Did you tell them to bring you back something from Congress though? Baduktopia should be there, so they should get you Lee Sedol’s new second book. =P
And on that note, I hear that Go Congress 2014 might be in NYC! So we should try to go! =)
